%% Diagram: Submission lifecycle
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant F as Form runtime
    participant S as Server
    participant DB as Draft store

    U->>F: Submit
    F->>F: Run client validators (suggestive)
    alt client invalid
        F-->>U: Show errors, focus first
    else client valid
        F->>F: Generate Idempotency-Key (UUIDv4)
        F->>S: POST /submit + Idempotency-Key + payload
        alt 200 OK
            S-->>F: Receipt
            F->>DB: delete(formId)
            F-->>U: Success state
        else 422 application/problem+json
            S-->>F: { errors:[{ pointer, detail }] }
            F->>F: Map JSON Pointers to field paths
            F-->>U: Show server errors, focus first
        else 409 Conflict / network error
            F->>F: Backoff + retry with same key
            F->>S: POST /submit + same Idempotency-Key
        end
    end
